title: LF Diamond 5+ Jungle for 5s
body:
Hey guys, looking to take 5s fairly seriously this season. Reaching diamond shouldn't take long and our focus is on reaching master this season. Looking for a diamond jungle main to join our team and climb the ranks with us; preferably someone with a great sense of humour and someone who doesn't get salty if you're having a bad game :)

Add me in game for more information.
